Package: prlm
Title: Pseudo-observation Regularized LM
Version: 1.0.2
Authors@R: 
    person("George", "Berry", , "george.e.berry@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Use lm in R adding while pseudo-observations to regularize every coefficient towards zero. prlm implements lm exactly except it adds an identity matrix to the X variables and a vector of 0's to the y variable.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
